<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Unlock Your Account</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #4b5563;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7 0%, #fed7aa 100%);
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: white;
        border-radius: 24px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        margin-top: 40px;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
      }

      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d97706 0%, #b45309 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 48px 32px;
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .header::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: -50%;
        left: -50%;
        width: 200%;
        height: 200%;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
        animation: pulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
      }

      @keyframes pulse {
        0%, 100% { opacity: 0.5; }
        50% { opacity: 0.8; }
      }

      .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 32px;
        font-weight: 700;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
      }

      .header-icon {
        width: 64px;
        height: 64px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        border-radius: 16px;
        margin: 0 auto 16px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 28px;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 40px 32px;
        background: white;
      }

      .content h2 {
        color: #1f2937;
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin: 0 0 24px 0;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .email-info {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7 0%, #fed7aa 100%);
        border: 1px solid #fbbf24;
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 24px;
        margin: 24px 0;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .email-address {
        color: #d97706;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 18px;
      }

      .lock-info {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef2f2 0%, #fee2e2 100%);
        border: 2px solid #ef4444;
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 24px;
        margin: 24px 0;
        border-left: 6px solid #ef4444;
        position: relative;
      }

      .lock-info::before {
        content: '🚫';
        position: absolute;
        top: -12px;
        left: 24px;
        background: #ef4444;
        color: white;
        width: 32px;
        height: 32px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      .lock-info h3 {
        color: #dc2626;
        margin: 0 0 12px 0;
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .lock-info p {
        color: #dc2626;
        margin: 0;
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      .unlock-reasons {
        background: #f8fafc;
        border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 24px;
        margin: 24px 0;
      }

      .unlock-reasons h3 {
        color: #1e293b;
        margin: 0 0 16px 0;
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 600;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
      }

      .reasons-list {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
      }

      .reasons-list li {
        background: white;
        border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 12px 16px;
        margin: 8px 0;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 12px;
        color: #374151;
      }

      .reason-icon {
        font-size: 16px;
        flex-shrink: 0;
      }

      .button-container {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 32px 0;
      }

      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 16px 32px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d97706 0%, #b45309 100%);
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 16px;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.3);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }

      .button:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.4);
      }

      .link-fallback {
        background: #f9fafb;
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 16px;
        margin: 16px 0;
        word-break: break-all;
      }

      .link-fallback-label {
        color: #6b7280;
        font-size: 14px;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }

      .link-fallback-url {
        color: #d97706;
        font-weight: 500;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .footer {
        padding: 32px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #6b7280;
        font-size: 14px;
        background: #f9fafb;
        border-top: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
      }

      .footer p {
        margin: 8px 0;
      }

      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .container {
          margin: 20px;
          border-radius: 16px;
        }

        .header {
          padding: 32px 24px;
        }

        .content {
          padding: 24px 20px;
        }

        .header h1 {
          font-size: 24px;
        }

        .content h2 {
          font-size: 22px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="header-icon">🔓</div>
        <h1>Account Unlock</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <h2>Your Account Was Locked</h2>

        <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 18px; color: #1f2937; margin: 24px 0;">
          Your account has been locked due to security reasons, but don't worry - we can unlock it right away.
        </p>

        <div class="email-info">
          <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; color: #6b7280;">Locked account:</p>
          <div class="email-address"><%= @resource.email %></div>
        </div>

        <div class="lock-info">
          <h3>Why was my account locked?</h3>
          <p>Your account was automatically locked as a security measure. This typically happens after multiple unsuccessful sign-in attempts.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="unlock-reasons">
          <h3>🛡️ Account locks help protect you from:</h3>
          <ul class="reasons-list">
            <li>
              <span class="reason-icon">🔐</span>
              Unauthorized access attempts
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="reason-icon">🤖</span>
              Automated brute force attacks
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="reason-icon">👥</span>
              Identity theft and fraud
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 18px; color: #1f2937; margin: 24px 0;">
          Click the button below to unlock your account:
        </p>

        <div class="button-container">
          <a href="<%= unlock_url(@resource, unlock_token: @token) %>" class="button">Unlock My Account</a>
        </div>

        <div class="link-fallback">
          <div class="link-fallback-label">Or copy and paste this link into your browser:</div>
          <div class="link-fallback-url"><%= unlock_url(@resource, unlock_token: @token) %></div>
        </div>

        <p style="color: #6b7280; text-align: center; margin-top: 24px;">
          If you didn't try to sign in recently, please contact our support team immediately.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>This email was sent because your account was locked for security reasons.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
